<PageInfo title="Rotating in fixed amounts"/>

<xPageTitle>
	Rotating in fixed amounts
</xPageTitle>

<p>
	Most of the camera rotation commands only rotate by fixed amounts (initially
	10 degree increments). To change the angles that the camera rotates:
</p>

<ol>
	<li>
		Press the <xButtonGridSelect/> button.
	</li>
	<li>
		A popup menu wil appear.
		Select the angle (at the bottom of the menu) that you wish to use.
	</li>
</ol>

